Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.26,0:00:08.90,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,So, I was waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:11.03,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What the hell is he planning?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.49,0:00:14.41,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Work with me and become a mangaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.20,0:00:20.16,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I–I'm going to be drawing the art, and he's doing the stories.
