Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.37,0:00:23.54,Main,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Then I'm sure you'll make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.12,0:00:27.17,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,S-So if our manga gets turned into an anime,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.17,0:00:29.45,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,we'll reserve the role of heroine for you or something...
