Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.44,0:00:31.55,Main,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.55,0:00:33.26,Main,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.26,0:00:36.43,Main,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll become a seiyuu and appear on your anime.
