Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.72,0:06:52.55,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Azuki...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.97,0:06:58.22,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's the same as always.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.22,0:07:00.06,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even after something like what happened last night...{\i0}
