Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.98,0:07:06.11,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I become a mangaka...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.11,0:07:08.65,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dreams... marriage...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.03,0:07:10.65,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Me, marrying Azuki?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.32,0:07:15.33,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't do this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.11,0:07:17.56,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.56,0:07:18.62,Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Mashiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:22.83,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel so good, could I rest in the infirmary until second period?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:25.29,Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Your complexion certainly doesn't look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.21,0:07:28.84,Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,You can take a retest, if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:29.92,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.76,0:07:33.55,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I finished half, this much will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:37.43,Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay to go on your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.43,0:07:38.52,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.89,0:07:44.85,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, me too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.85,0:07:48.07,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I spent all last night studying and now I feel dizzy. Can I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.48,0:07:50.16,Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,What? You too, Takagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.16,0:07:52.07,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I finished the test!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:53.74,Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess it's all right then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:57.08,Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now, everybody concentrate on your tests!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:07:59.99,TS,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\b1\c&H60615F&\frz6.736\fscx110\fscy95\pos(524,358)}Infirmary
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:01.96,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.58,0:08:04.42,Main,Nurse,0000,0000,0000,,What? You too, Takagi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.44,0:08:06.87,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I didn't get enough sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.87,0:08:08.76,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just be borrowing a bed for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.76,0:08:11.05,Main,Nurse,0000,0000,0000,,You really don't look it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.11,0:08:14.45,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so dizzy I feel like I'm gonna throw up, I've got a migraine...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.45,0:08:15.51,Main,Nurse,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.26,0:08:17.51,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Saikou?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.05,0:08:19.22,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seriously annoying.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:22.10,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't sleep last night, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.10,0:08:24.64,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Have you eaten? Do you have a fever or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.95,0:08:29.09,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,It was kind of suffocating, being in that classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:30.61,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Suffocating?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.61,0:08:31.69,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,From lack of sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.60,0:08:38.24,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,It's like my chest got all tight when I was in the same room as Azuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.46,0:08:41.84,Main,Nurse,0000,0000,0000,,Are you two fooling around?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.84,0:08:43.00,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.62,0:08:48.08,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Your chest felt tight?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.08,0:08:50.92,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Has there been any progress since then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.92,0:08:51.88,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,No, none.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:08:54.09,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,"None?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.09,0:08:56.18,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you guys at least exchange email addresses?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.18,0:08:57.22,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,No, we didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:09:01.89,Main,Nurse,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! If you're well enough to talk, then please go back to your classroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.43,0:09:05.39,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,We can't talk here. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.39,0:09:06.39,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Fine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.19,0:09:08.68,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.69,0:09:10.02,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,We're going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:13.07,Main,Nurse,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you two come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:18.11,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask for Azuki's address for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.11,0:09:22.04,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I'd feel pretty pathetic if you did that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.04,0:09:23.79,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't ask her yourself, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:29.38,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,If I could talk to her that easily, I wouldn't be stressing over this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:31.88,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Saikou...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.17,0:09:37.18,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,You really do like Azuki, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.12,0:09:40.60,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I like people like you two, Saikou.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.60,0:09:42.76,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,You're as creepy as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.72,0:09:46.77,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Look at other people who are going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.77,0:09:48.87,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,They're being lovey dovey without caring where they are,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.87,0:09:51.77,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,they prattle on about how proud they are to be dating and stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.31,0:09:54.15,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,They're all just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.15,0:10:00.67,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to them, I like people who get choked up from just being in the same classroom way better.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.67,0:10:03.49,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, what good does it do me to be liked by you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.43,0:10:07.74,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,But now it's really sealed that we'll team up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.74,0:10:08.99,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.99,0:10:12.54,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm the only one who knows that you like Azuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.54,0:10:13.26,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.26,0:10:14.80,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell anybody, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:17.80,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm the only one who you can talk to about your love life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.09,0:10:19.55,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,We're each other's closest friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.55,0:10:21.97,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,So let's combine our skills in both love and manga and give it everything we've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.81,0:10:25.97,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Love is love, manga is manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.44,0:10:27.84,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.85,0:10:31.52,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, are you okay with not going back? There's still time—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:34.88,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I already finished the test flawlessly, full marks without a doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.98,0:10:37.32,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.94,0:10:41.24,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got your sights set on being a mangaka, so why are you studying so hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:42.45,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need an academic background for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.59,0:10:44.63,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.63,0:10:47.54,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Even I'm not a hundred percent sure I can make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.00,0:10:51.71,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought... That's a wise way to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.79,0:10:55.71,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Do you see everyone in the class as idiots?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.71,0:10:56.80,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.81,0:10:59.41,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you're the smartest one in the class?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.41,0:11:02.22,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Why such an unpleasant question all of a sudden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:03.51,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,So you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.05,0:11:06.18,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,As for being a mangaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.18,0:11:08.72,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You think that unless you're smart, you can't become one, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.23,0:11:11.56,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:14.86,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,To be a mangaka, you need brains and good sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.86,0:11:18.53,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't think you can say "being good at studying equals being smart."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.48,0:11:23.23,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,It's only been two months since we joined the same class, Saikou,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.23,0:11:25.58,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,but I knew it as soon as I saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:27.95,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,"This guy's smart."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.95,0:11:30.25,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I asked you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.25,0:11:31.91,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If it were only your drawings that were good, I wouldn't have asked you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:36.42,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,As for that "Do you see everyone in the class as idiots?" question...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:39.37,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you see everyone you asked it as idiots themselves, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.62,0:11:42.30,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Azuki's smart too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:43.80,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, I think she's clever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.22,0:11:47.68,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,She's cute, but without standing out in an odd way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.68,0:11:50.47,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,She genuinely behaves with grace, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.49,0:11:52.39,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}It's because she's doing it without thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.85,0:11:56.06,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1050)}I think she's much cleverer than me, who can just study well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.06,0:11:58.48,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,You saw Azuki's house, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.28,0:12:01.28,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:04.49,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,She's even blessed in her own environment and household, that Azuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.49,0:12:07.69,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she's not greedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.70,0:12:12.10,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Azuki's charm comes from her good family and wealth of spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.10,0:12:14.12,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,and she has a dignity born of her intelligence, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:16.78,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Dignity, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.79,0:12:19.00,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you sure are praising her a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:22.59,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I may be praising her, but you're not getting jealous or impatient.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.30,0:12:24.55,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you're smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.76,0:12:31.35,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Man, good parents, a good house, a good face,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.37,0:12:33.82,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,from the moment we're born, there's plenty of stuff that makes everyone different.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.61,0:12:38.02,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,But in the end, past all that, the stupid ones who dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.02,0:12:41.60,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,750)}but are smart enough not to get lost in their dreams, are the ones who can get to the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:43.99,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.78,0:12:51.74,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, from this point onwards, we've gotta keep giving it all we've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:54.16,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Shuujin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.37,0:12:57.71,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I think I might team up with you after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:01.71,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Your way of thinking is sort of similar to mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:04.13,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,and I think a story made by you would be interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:05.72,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:07.50,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's both do our best together!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.50,0:13:09.21,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I said "might."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.22,0:13:11.60,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I just mean that if you write a {\i1}name{\i0} that is interesting,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:13.39,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll draw the pictures for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.39,0:13:14.27,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.44,0:13:22.36,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,First period is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.36,0:13:23.94,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you can handle taking the next exam?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.08,0:13:35.16,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,So what's a "{\i1}name{\i0}?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.16,0:13:36.08,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.89,0:13:59.27,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking about your uncle's suicide, like you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.22,0:14:04.19,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think your parents would be against you becoming a mangaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.13,0:14:07.19,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,With something like that having happened to a relative,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:09.74,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,it wouldn't be that strange for them to be opposed to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:14.29,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's certainly true that since Uncle died like that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.29,0:14:15.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They'll definitely be against the idea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.70,0:14:18.58,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,When I get home, I'll convince them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.46,0:14:23.38,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Like with Kyojin no Hoshi's Hoshi Ittetsu
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.38,0:14:25.80,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,and Oishinbo's Kaibara Yuuzan,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.26,0:14:29.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,parents are the first hurdle for their kids to overcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.97,0:14:32.85,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The rules in my house are like this:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:35.89,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's something I want or something I need to discuss,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:37.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I talk to Mom first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:41.73,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, when I'm not around, my mom tells my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.06,0:14:46.28,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Then if my dad is against it, she'll tell me later.
