Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.36,0:14:51.16,TS,Cut Plaque,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\fs10\bord0\shad2\4c&HC6C6C8&\fnEngravers MT\frz353.98\move(1064,564,1176,564)\c&H444346&}Mashiro Masahiro
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.83,0:14:50.13,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If no objections are made, then that means it's okay and goes through.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:55.08,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, my dad and I have almost never had a serious talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.79,0:14:58.25,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.25,0:15:01.26,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I will when it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.38,0:15:01.26,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:03.54,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.54,0:15:05.25,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't even said "I'm home" yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.54,0:15:06.84,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got something I need to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.50,0:15:21.53,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? What do you need to discuss?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.53,0:15:23.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.65,0:15:27.07,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please hurry up and say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.07,0:15:27.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.44,0:15:30.61,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be a mangaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.78,0:15:31.40,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.90,0:15:34.16,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That sure was a fast reply.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.99,0:15:37.12,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go to high school and college, like normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.12,0:15:39.36,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If nothing comes of it by the time I'm out of college, I'll give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.70,0:15:43.42,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,By that you mean you'll settle for any old school and just draw manga, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:47.38,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even your uncle had his debut when he was in college.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.38,0:15:49.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I let you do this here, you'd just be doing the same thing as him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.46,0:15:52.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I knew there'd be a comparison to Uncle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.19,0:15:52.32,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about manga and concentrate on your studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:55.68,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know for sure that I'd go down the same path that Uncle did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.68,0:15:57.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's definitely no reason to think I'd kill myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:16:00.35,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think your uncle committed suicide?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.10,0:16:03.14,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your uncle over-exerted himself—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.14,0:16:04.52,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:07.61,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn't selling anymore, and in order to get selling again, he worked too hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.61,0:16:10.82,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I meant that to draw until you die is like suicide, in a way...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.07,0:16:13.65,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.65,0:16:16.57,Main,,0000,0000,0000,, I'm sure your father wouldn't allow it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.99,0:16:18.53,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, end of discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.95,0:16:21.16,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.16,0:16:21.86,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.11,0:16:25.74,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please at least talk with Dad about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.09,0:16:39.68,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad still hasn't come home yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:26.69,TS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\frz38.728\c&H101819&\b1\fs56\fnKomika Text Kaps\pos(620,625)}SUPER
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.35,0:17:30.27,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.65,0:17:33.57,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Manga sure is amazing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.36,0:17:39.66,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Though I said it in the spur of the moment, I've always wanted to be a mangaka...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.74,0:17:40.99,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,150)\i1}like Uncle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.99,0:17:43.83,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Uncle was always drawing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.66,0:17:46.62,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1500)\i1}As he kept drawing he'd get more disheveled.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.00,0:17:50.54,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He may not have been able to sell in the end,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.13,0:17:53.09,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and he may be gone now,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.75,0:17:56.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but this fascinating manga is still here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.55,0:18:00.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think, after all, no matter what I'm told,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.52,0:18:02.20,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,even if I'm disowned,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.20,0:18:03.71,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to become a mangaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.47,0:18:06.76,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.76,0:18:09.05,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,700)}Dad's... home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.74,0:18:23.08,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ten minutes... No, five minutes?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.37,0:18:25.20,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was fast.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:27.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Must mean Dad gave a fast reply too...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.43,0:18:30.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Moritaka, I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:31.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.76,0:18:38.22,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I talked to your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.13,0:18:40.47,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.68,0:18:48.14,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Let him do it."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.14,0:18:52.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Men have their dreams that women can't understand."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.11,0:18:54.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is what he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.99,0:19:03.16,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.16,0:19:04.12,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.12,0:19:05.91,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,To your grandfather's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.57,0:19:11.44,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one who lost a son to manga, so we have to let him know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:13.29,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll tell him yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.29,0:19:17.38,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.79,0:19:26.95,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.95,0:19:28.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,can I come in for a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.45,0:19:29.56,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.52,0:19:33.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.24,0:19:35.69,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Moritaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.69,0:19:38.57,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be a mangaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.01,0:19:43.48,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh, a mangaka eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.48,0:19:44.75,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.92,0:19:59.21,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Moritaka, take this with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.63,0:20:00.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,A key?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.46,0:20:01.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.72,0:20:08.01,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this... your answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.03,0:20:09.28,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.28,0:20:11.22,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are these keys?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.32,0:20:15.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The keys to your uncle's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.82,0:20:23.90,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobihiro's room, his workplace has been left the same as it was when he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.90,0:20:25.70,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's yours, Moritaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.24,0:20:29.28,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I haven't decided if I want to become a mangaka for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.28,0:20:31.62,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still ten years too early to have a workplace...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.63,0:20:33.22,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.79,0:20:38.46,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be using it seriously for a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.46,0:20:42.55,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,but there's nothing wrong with being prepared ahead of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:49.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, that room is packed with things you need to become a mangaka, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.97,0:20:52.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Do you not need it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.86,0:21:04.19,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.40,0:21:06.70,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it all right if I go over there now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.87,0:21:08.12,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:10.66,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's past ten already and you have a test tomorrow—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.66,0:21:11.91,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.54,0:21:15.08,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.54,0:21:17.71,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, I'm gonna get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.00,0:21:21.46,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.46,0:21:24.42,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Moritaka has changed, hasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.42,0:21:29.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,450)}I was really worried that he'd end up a failure,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.39,0:21:32.14,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,but he's fine like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.36,0:21:42.61,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just seeing Uncle's manuscripts will be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.98,0:21:46.24,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.95,0:21:48.86,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.45,0:21:56.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.50,0:22:05.09,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle's workplace...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.10,0:22:06.54,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been three years...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.26,0:22:16.77,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoohoo, my beloved Saikou-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.77,0:22:18.14,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did your parents give you permission?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.44,0:22:20.48,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you a {\i1}name{\i0}, so come.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.48,0:22:21.35,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.35,0:22:23.19,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I got my uncle's workplace!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.15,0:22:26.99,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I got the workplace that my uncle left after he died!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.99,0:22:31.11,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Do you mean they gave it to you when you said you were going to be a mangaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.13,0:22:31.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.79,0:22:32.99,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.99,0:22:33.94,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.94,0:22:36.41,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm heading towards the northern Yakusa Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.53,0:22:37.93,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The workplace is in Yakusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.93,0:22:39.96,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! One stop huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.96,0:22:42.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving right now, wait for me at the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.22,0:22:43.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.05,0:24:20.85,TS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\b1\pos(1062,255)}Preview of \NNext Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.70,0:24:17.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to Uncle's workplace!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.91,0:24:21.09,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's left behind there are passionate thoughts and a harsh reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.09,0:24:22.74,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And the shocking truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.74,0:24:23.85,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna know!
Dialogue: 1,0:24:23.02,0:24:29.97,TS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\bord1.5\b1\pos(241,523)}Parents\Nand Children
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.85,0:24:25.48,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Parents and Children
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.48,0:24:28.04,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What supports dreams are love and romance!
